843
00:39:25,450 --> 00:39:27,680
I find this quite puzzling.

844
00:39:29,530 --> 00:39:30,720
My surname is Yan.

845
00:39:33,970 --> 00:39:36,050
Look at me, I forgot about that.

846
00:39:37,160 --> 00:39:37,600
So.

