00:39:58,760 --> 00:39:59,410
Duanwu,

851
00:39:59,800 --> 00:40:00,450
let me ask you,

852
00:40:01,090 --> 00:40:02,800
the day after the Pearl Tower burned,

853
00:40:03,490 --> 00:40:05,160
