00:41:02,720 --> 00:41:03,370
Duanwu.

864
00:41:13,930 --> 00:41:14,530
Duanwu,

865
00:41:15,200 --> 00:41:16,680
do you realize aiding a murderer

866
00:41:17,200 --> 00:41:18,370
